TikTok is actually banned for a much more major reason than only grabbing clipboard data. The code of that application is designed in such a way that no matter how you control your location permissions, it somehow grabs your exact location everytime. One indian youtuber/instagrammer pointed out that this application directly grabs the location from your SIM CARD. 
Man what would it take in this world to be actually free and not be surveiled all the time.
